    "MEMKGC [67] predicts the masked entities of the triple.",
    "StAR [68] utilizes Siamese textual encoders to separately encode the entities.",
    "GenKGC [69] uses the decoder-only language models to directly generate the tail entity.",
    "TagReal [70] generates high-quality prompts from the external text corpora.",
    "AutoKG [63] directly adopts the LLMs, such as ChatGPT and GPT-4, and designs tailored 123 prompts to predict the tail entity."
